; Coverage test for filters.cc early return in by_payee_posts
; When inserting into payee_subtotals fails (already exists), the early
; return is triggered. In practice, the insert always
; succeeds for new payees (asserted), but this test exercises the
; by_payee_posts path generally. Also covers the normal flush

2024/01/01 Shop
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/02/01 Shop
    Expenses:Food    $20.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/03/01 Restaurant
    Expenses:Food    $50.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --by-payee
24-Mar-01 Restaurant            Assets:Cash                 $-50.00      $-50.00
                                Expenses:Food                $50.00            0
24-Jan-01 Shop                  Assets:Cash                 $-30.00      $-30.00
                                Expenses:Food                $30.00            0
end test
